for linux first use command 
sudo apt install ufw 
sudo ufw enable
sudo ufw allow 22/tcp  (t0 allow 22 port)
after running all the commands we will get this result 

     To                         Action      From
     --                         ------      ----
[ 1] 22/tcp                     ALLOW IN    Anywhere                  
[ 2] 80/tcp                     ALLOW IN    Anywhere                  
[ 3] 21/tcp                     DENY IN     Anywhere                  
[ 4] 22/tcp (v6)                ALLOW IN    Anywhere (v6)             
[ 5] 80/tcp (v6)                ALLOW IN    Anywhere (v6)             
[ 6] 21/tcp (v6)                DENY IN     Anywhere (v6)             
